---
// Component to recreate the Course Features section exactly like the original
---

<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center" style="color: #1e293b;">課程特色</h2>
    
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <!-- Infographic Section - Left side -->
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <img 
          src="/src/assets/images/school-courses/Scratch 人工智能編程/ai-five-concepts.webp" 
          alt="AI 五大理念"
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Features List - Right side -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
            <span class="text-gray-900">•</span>
            <span>了解 <a href="https://medium.com/10botics/ai-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E7%90%86%E5%BF%B5-%E7%B5%A6k12%E5%AD%A9%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%84ai%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-44a4aafc03fb" class="text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-600">AI 五大理念</a>，趨勢與實踐</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
            <span class="text-gray-900">•</span>
            <span>認識機器學習 (Machine Learning) 的類別</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
            <span class="text-gray-900">•</span>
            <span>透過 Teachable Machine 訓練人工智能模型，並結合 Scratch 製作不同的 AI 應用程式</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
            <span class="text-gray-900">•</span>
            <span>讓學生體驗與 AI 互動</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Demo Video Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="aspect-video bg-black rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg mb-4">
          <iframe 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OoTX6U_aVto?controls=1&rel=0"
            class="w-full h-full"
            frameborder="0"
            allowfullscreen
            title="Scratch AI Project - Mask Detector">
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">輕易與 Teachable Machine 連結，讓學生發揮創意，實現所想</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI Recognition Examples - match original layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Face Recognition -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <img 
          src="https://lwfiles.mycourse.app/10botics-public/bf6bae32bf18a9afffdf2ef18615f8f9.gif" 
          alt="人面識別" 
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">人面識別</h3>
      </div>

      <!-- Gesture Recognition -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <img 
          src="https://lwfiles.mycourse.app/10botics-public/c98ce8ccb7da82373fec7c244b34a9b3.gif" 
          alt="手勢識別" 
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">手勢識別</h3>
      </div>

      <!-- Pose Recognition -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <img 
          src="https://lwfiles.mycourse.app/10botics-public/fa5eab50642474658210ee6ba7029e31.gif" 
          alt="姿勢識別" 
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
        />
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">姿勢識別</h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 